01:28:25.666 --> 01:28:28.476
- Counsel, please be seated.
- ...alienating him from his father,

01:28:28.500 --> 01:28:31.460
which has turned Charlie's world
upside down.

01:28:31.541 --> 01:28:33.309
- Counselor?
