01:32:15.583 --> 01:32:17.003
I think he wants it too much.

01:32:17.083 --> 01:32:19.003
They said he's off the charts in math.

01:32:19.083 --> 01:32:21.476
He quits too easily
when things aren't easy for him.

01:32:21.500 --> 01:32:23.170
You know, he's like us, he's stubborn.

01:32:24.000 --> 01:32:27.250
He's still a lousy Monopoly player
because he tries to save all his money.

01:32:32.708 --> 01:32:33.708
So...

01:32:34.833 --> 01:32:37.463
- I thought we should talk.
- Mm-hmm.

01:32:37.541 --> 01:32:39.581
I feel like maybe things
have gone too far.

01:32:39.625 --> 01:32:40.455
Uh-huh.

01:32:40.541 --> 01:32:43.791
I mean, my mom's taking out a loan
against the house to help me pay Nora.

01:32:43.875 --> 01:32:45.165
I thought I paid Nora.

01:32:45.250 --> 01:32:46.960
